						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the middle of a road.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Suratāṇa Mahāmaṁḍa 1331 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It is damaged and illegible and mentions Suratāna Mahamaṁḍa • • • • • It records the grant of a shop <hi rend="italic">(aṁgaḍi)</hi> free from all taxes to <hi rend="italic">heggaḍe</hi> Mādiseṭṭi.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1253, Prajāpati, Śrāvaṇa Śu. 5 Vaḍḍavara corresponding to 1331 A.D., July 10, Wednesday.</p>						

						</summary>
